ClearCase version 0.01
======================

This is an early version of an OO perl interface to ClearCase.  It handles
types, views, vobs etc. well but does not yet handle versions, branches or
elements well.  This is alpha software - any part of the interface may
change at any time.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Memoize  (included in Perl 5.8)

